{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1773351696039,"sessionID":"ses_31c00ea90ffeMcRFqNZY7ExB1k","part":{"id":"prt_ce3ff74c6001A0AMPmhr5GfKmg","sessionID":"ses_31c00ea90ffeMcRFqNZY7ExB1k","messageID":"msg_ce3ff4ab5001RpPa2czU2w0YcZ","type":"tool","callID":"toolu_vrtx_01ARhn4FqdBet8F6Hb1mYo7h","tool":"bash","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"bun src/index.ts --version 2>&1","description":"Test --version flag"},"output":"wombo 0.0.9\n","title":"Test --version flag","metadata":{"output":"wombo 0.0.9\n","exit":0,"description":"Test --version flag","truncated":false},"time":{"start":1773351695927,"end":1773351696038}}}}
{"type":"text","timestamp":1773351696424,"sessionID":"ses_31c00ea90ffeMcRFqNZY7ExB1k","part":{"id":"prt_ce3ff52ee0012i2Y0gtYG6WfX1","sessionID":"ses_31c00ea90ffeMcRFqNZY7ExB1k","messageID":"msg_ce3ff4ab5001RpPa2czU2w0YcZ","type":"text","text":"Now let me analyze the current state. Looking at the code:\n\n1. **--version flag**: Already partially handled at line 428-438 (`if (args.command === \"--version\" || args.command === \"-V\")`). However, looking at the `parseArgs` function, lines 233-235 show that `--version` is parsed as a flag that consumes the next arg as a version string (for the `upgrade` command). This means `wombo --version` sets `args.command` to `--version` which IS handled. But `wombo -V` would also work since it falls through to `args.command` being `-V`. Let me verify what actually happens when someone types `wombo --version`:\n\nLooking more carefully:\n- `args[0]` would be `--version`, so `args.command = \"--version\"` \n- Then in `parseArgs`, the loop starts at `startIdx = 1`, so the `--version` at position 0 isn't hit by the switch case\n- In `main()`, line 428 checks `args.command === \"--version\" || args.command === \"-V\"` — this IS already handled\n\nWait, but what about `-V`? If you type `wombo -V`, `args[0]` would be `-V`, and `args.command = \"-V\"`. Then line 428 checks for `-V` — so this IS already handled too.\n\nLet me test to make sure:","time":{"start":1773351696424,"end":1773351696424}}}
