{"type":"text","timestamp":1773351892693,"sessionID":"ses_31c00ea90ffeMcRFqNZY7ExB1k","part":{"id":"prt_ce4025865001giMcKeUA3ZWbvv","sessionID":"ses_31c00ea90ffeMcRFqNZY7ExB1k","messageID":"msg_ce4025122001X2ShDq4On8ZgA0","type":"text","text":"All tasks complete. Here's a summary of what was done:\n\n## Summary\n\n### Subtask 1: `--version / -V` flag (`feat(cli-ux-polish)`)\n- The `--version` and `-V` flags were already implemented in main (handling them as commands in `main()`). \n- **Refinement**: Replaced `readFileSync` + `JSON.parse` with `Bun.file().json()` to follow the project convention of preferring Bun APIs. Added null coalescing for the version field.\n\n### Subtask 2: Fix misleading `--all-ready` message (`fix(cli-ux-polish)`)\n- The context-aware message splitting was already in place from main.\n- **Improvement**: Enhanced both error messages to be more actionable:\n  - `--all-ready` path: Changed to definitive phrasing (\"all features are done, cancelled, or have unmet dependencies\") and suggests running `wombo features list` to review.\n  - Non-`--all-ready` path: Improved to suggest both `--all-ready` flag and `wombo features list --ready` for checking available features.\n\n### Build Verification\n- `bun run typecheck` passes cleanly\n- `bun run build` succeeds (0.77 MB bundle, 134 modules)\n- Functional tests confirm `wombo --version` and `wombo -V` both print `wombo 0.0.9`","time":{"start":1773351892692,"end":1773351892692}}}
